data.description: Must see this beautiful property located near major Disney World attractions, restaurants, medical offices, and hospitals. This amazing home has 3 bedrooms, and 2 bathrooms. Home is completed! Home was built in 2000! Home is recently update with new Roof and beautiful fresh paint. This could be the perfect vacation home for you and your family, perfect investment property, or simply the perfect for ever home. Get ready to enjoy this amazing Florida home. The community is really Friedly and safe! The community offer tremendous amenities such as community pool.
